    "description": {
      "value": "Endeavor Vietnam is the Vietnam office of Endeavor, the leading global community of, by, and for High-Impact Entrepreneurs. It selects, mentors, and accelerates the fastest-growing founders in Vietnam through its flagship Scale Up Program, Endeavor AI Lab, and the Endeavor Entrepreneur selection process. Endeavor Vietnam provides entrepreneurs access to a global network of mentors, investors, and partners, and co-invests through the Endeavor Catalyst fund. The organization screens 100k+ companies globally, and its Vietnam portfolio includes unicorns such as Sky Mavis, alongside high-growth companies like Trusting Social (fintech), Scommerce (logistics), Katalon (enterprise SaaS), NextPay (fintech), and OnPoint (e-commerce).",
